Paper: hep-th/9610192

Date: 1996-10-24

Title: The Frobenius-Schur indicator in Conformal Field Theory

Authors: Peter Bantay

Comments: 5 pages, TeX, some typos corrected

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B394 (1997) 87-88

An analogue of the classical Frobenius-Schur indicator is introduced in orderto distinguish between real and pseudo-real self-conjugate primary fields, andan explicit expression for this quantity is derived from the trace of thebraiding operator.